            <title>
                <![CDATA[中本聪再度现身推特？遭打脸：帐号早已被澳本聪接管]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">一个沈寂 5 年的「中本聪」推特帐号在前日凌晨再度活跃，多则推文倡导比特币白皮书的重要性，并指出比特币减半是一个重要的预期事件。然而，该帐号早已被证实，是由自称是中本聪、但从未提出具体证据的「澳本聪」Craig Wright 所管理。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/satoshi-nakamoto-twitter-account-craig-wright#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-651d0936199bc"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-651d0936199bc"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/satoshi-nakamoto-twitter-account-craig-wright/#%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%AC%E8%81%B0%E7%8F%BE%E8%B9%A4%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9%EF%BC%9F" title="中本聪现踪推特？">中本聪现踪推特？</a><ul class="ez-toc-list-level-3"><li class="ez-toc-heading-level-3"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/satoshi-nakamoto-twitter-account-craig-wright/#%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98%E9%87%90%E6%B8%85%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E5%81%87%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F" title="社群笔记厘清：这是假帐号">社群笔记厘清：这是假帐号</a></li></ul></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/satoshi-nakamoto-twitter-account-craig-wright/#%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E5%81%87%E5%86%92%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F" title="社群呼吁：删除假冒帐号">社群呼吁：删除假冒帐号</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4" href="https://abmedia.io/satoshi-nakamoto-twitter-account-craig-wright/#%E6%BE%B3%E6%9C%AC%E8%81%B0%E9%81%B2%E9%81%B2%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E" title="澳本聪迟迟无法提出证明">澳本聪迟迟无法提出证明</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5" href="https://abmedia.io/satoshi-nakamoto-twitter-account-craig-wright/#%E8%AA%B0%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%AC%E8%81%B0%EF%BC%9F" title="谁才是中本聪？">谁才是中本聪？</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%AC%E8%81%B0%E7%8F%BE%E8%B9%A4%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9%EF%BC%9F"></span>中本聪现踪推特？<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>前天晚上，名为 @satoshi 的推特帐号睽违 5 年再度发布推文，引发社群议论，距离上次发文已是 2018 年 10 月。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Bitcoin is a predicate machine.  Over the following months, we shall explore different aspects that were not explicitly contained within the white paper.  These aspects are all parts of bitcoin, and are important.  Some of these ideas were touched upon in the early years; now is…</p><p>— Satoshi Nakamoto (@satoshi) <a href="https://twitter.com/satoshi/status/1708886029636137256?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 2, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt">内容写道：「比特币是谓词机器 (predicate machine)。」并声称他将</span><span style="font-size: 12pt">在接下来的几个月里，探索比特币白皮书的不同面向。</span></p><h3><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98%E9%87%90%E6%B8%85%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E5%81%87%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F"></span>社群笔记厘清：这是假帐号<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h3><p>从推文下方的社群笔记可看出，该内容已被标示并确认与澳本聪 Craig Wright 有关，并非中本聪本人帐号。</p><p class="content">这不是真正的比特币创造者中本聪，该帐号与 Craig Wright 有关，他自称是中本聪，但没有任何实质证据。</p><p>前 nChain CEO Christen Ager-Hanssen，也公开表示该 @satoshi 帐户早已被澳本聪 Craig Wright 接管。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Isn’t it a coincident that <a href="https://twitter.com/satoshi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@satoshi</a> account is used during this time when I expose Craig?</p><p>That account has been taken over by Craig. The previous owner is a Craig Wright fanboy <a href="https://twitter.com/andyrowe?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@andyrowe</a></p><p>Don’t be fooled guys! <a href="https://t.co/4qtn8Dhx2P">pic.twitter.com/4qtn8Dhx2P</a></p><p>— Christen Ager-Hanssen (@agerhanssen) <a href="https://twitter.com/agerhanssen/status/1708911279044170050?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 2, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><p>他同时说明，该帐号甚至在上个月才<a href="https://twitter.com/agerhanssen/status/1708932728614166890" target="_blank" rel="noopener">付费验证其身份</a>，以获得蓝色标记图样。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E5%81%87%E5%86%92%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F"></span>社群呼吁：删除假冒帐号<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>针对此事，加密社群呼吁推特删除自称与比特币创造者中本聪有关的任何假冒帐号。</p><p><span class="css-901oao css-16my406 css-1hf3ou5 r-poiln3 r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0"><span class="css-901oao css-16my406 r-poiln3 r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0">用户 <a href="https://twitter.com/Pledditor/status/1708969096711127550" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pledditor</a> 怒批，自称为中本聪及名为「比特币」的帐号都应该被删除，因为它们违反了平台有关「误导及欺骗身份」的服务条款，无论该人的真实身份是否受到披露。</span></span></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E6%BE%B3%E6%9C%AC%E8%81%B0%E9%81%B2%E9%81%B2%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E"></span>澳本聪迟迟无法提出证明<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>一直以来，备受争议的 Craig Wright 都持续自称是比特币的创造者，但面对社群呼吁他利用公私钥签名核对的方式，来证明他拥有中本聪财产的所有权，他也对此<a href="https://twitter.com/theprojecttv/status/1556208056588976130" target="_blank" rel="noopener">多次逃避并回呛</a>：</p><p class="content">透过私钥证明资产所有权，就如同拿著你的车钥匙，说你的车是我的，是非常愚蠢且没有意义的。</p><p>此前，Craig Wright 于今年 2 月曾向英国法院提起版权<a href="https://decrypt.co/120884/craig-wright-loses-bitcoin-copyright-claim" target="_blank" rel="noopener">诉讼</a>，声称比特币网路的分叉侵犯了他的智慧财产权，但最终仍然败诉。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E8%AA%B0%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%AC%E8%81%B0%EF%BC%9F"></span>谁才是中本聪？<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>中本聪的真实身份一直为人津津乐道，也引发社会大众的猜测。</p><p>其中呼声最大的是具有电脑科学及密码学背景的&nbsp;<a href="https://twitter.com/halfin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hal Finney</a>，作为第一批运行比特币软体的人，他表明收到了中本聪所提供的第一笔比特币交易，其早期贡献者的身份被认为是中本聪本尊的候选人之一。</p><p><img class="alignnone  wp-image-80190" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hal.jpeg?resize=745%2C417&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="745" height="417" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hal.jpeg?w=1806&amp;ssl=1 1806w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hal.jpeg?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hal.jpeg?resize=1024%2C574&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hal.jpeg?resize=600%2C336&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hal.jpeg?resize=768%2C430&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hal.jpeg?resize=1536%2C861&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>同时，他在比特币创造后的几年里也持续活跃于社群，并多次透过论坛及社群媒体推广其理念与潜力，被视为是比特币发展的重要贡献人物。</p><p>然而，他在 10 年前罹患 ALS 疾病并接受采访时，早已对创造比特币的说法表示<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/andygreenberg/2014/03/25/satoshi-nakamotos-neighbor-the-bitcoin-ghostwriter-who-wasnt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">否认</a>，随后在 2014 年因并发症去世。</p><p>其他著名的推论包括曾开发出被认为是比特币前身「Bit Gold」的 <a href="https://abmedia.io/20111113-nick-szabo-s-view-on-ethereum" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nick Szabo</a>，与受到媒体断章取义的 <a href="https://www.newsweek.com/2014/03/14/face-behind-bitcoin-247957.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dorian Nakamoto</a> 等。</p><p>不过，事实是中本聪的确切身份仍然是个谜，上述人选纯属大众臆测。</p>
]]>
            </description>
