            <title>
                <![CDATA[SEC 上诉瑞波案遭驳回，Ripple（XRP）涨不动，已回到胜诉前水平]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/secs-motion-is-denied#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-651d0936247c9"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-651d0936247c9"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/secs-motion-is-denied/#SEC_%E6%8F%90%E4%B8%AD%E9%96%93%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E" title="SEC 提中间上诉遭驳回">SEC 提中间上诉遭驳回</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/secs-motion-is-denied/#%E7%91%9E%E6%B3%A2%E6%A1%88%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%8D%E5%AF%A9" title="瑞波案明年再审">瑞波案明年再审</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/secs-motion-is-denied/#XRP_%E5%B0%8F%E6%BC%B2_5" title="XRP 小涨 5%">XRP 小涨 5%</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="SEC_%E6%8F%90%E4%B8%AD%E9%96%93%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E"></span><strong>SEC 提中间上诉遭驳回</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>据法律文件，瑞波案主审法官 Analisa Torres 认为，SEC 未能履行上诉相关法规的职责，提出证明此前判决有法律问题或存在重大分歧的实质理由，已驳回 SEC 的中间上诉动议。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">SEC served another L in the Ripple case.  </p><p>They can’t appeal the decision until after a trial on remaining issues. <a href="https://t.co/t4rbAME1Cv">pic.twitter.com/t4rbAME1Cv</a></p><p>— Bill Hughes : wchughes.eth 🦊 (@BillHughesDC) <a href="https://twitter.com/BillHughesDC/status/1709345748930748708?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 3, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><p>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/ripple-xrp-case-explained" target="_blank" rel="noopener">读完 XRP 法院文件，详解 XRP 与币圈没有脱离证券风险的理由</a>)</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E7%91%9E%E6%B3%A2%E6%A1%88%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%8D%E5%AF%A9"></span><strong>瑞波案明年再审</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>ConsenSys 法律顾问 Bill Hughes 解释，瑞波案的简易判决是一项事实导向的裁决，并不适用于提出中间上诉，法官仅是说明 SEC 在此案无法证明主张，并不代表 SEC 在其它类似案件中都将会失败。</p><p>SEC 并非遭判死刑，法官将此案其它有待裁决的问题订于 2024 年 4 月进行审判，这包括陪审团判决将涵盖瑞波执行长 Brad Garlinghouse 及共同创办人 Chris Larsen，两人遭指控涉及 XRP 代币的非法证券发行，协助、教唆瑞波违反部分监管法规。</p><p>双方需在今年底 12 月 4 日前提交所有审前档案及相关证据。</p><p>SEC、瑞波发言人并未回应。</p><p><strong>注：在美国民事诉讼尚未完全结案、所有指控尚未获得裁定之前，一方提出上诉称之为中间上诉 (interlocutory appeal)，其中在仅在联邦法院、各州法院规定的特定情况下才允许中间上诉。</strong></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="XRP_%E5%B0%8F%E6%BC%B2_5"></span><strong>XRP 小涨 5%</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>XRP 在过去 24 小时上涨 5.23%，价格为 0.538 美元。</p><p>不过在 9 月中旬时，XRP 已正式跌回了胜诉前的 0.47 美元，此前 0.82 美元、近 100% 的涨幅已消失殆尽。</p><figure id="attachment_80171" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-80171" style="width: 595px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-80171 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-10-04-101852.png?resize=595%2C390&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="595" height="390" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕撷取画面-2023-10-04-101852.png?w=595&amp;ssl=1 595w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕撷取画面-2023-10-04-101852.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-80171" class="wp-caption-text">XRP 周线图｜来源：Investing.com</figcaption></figure><div id="gtx-trans" style="position: absolute; left: 452px; top: 977.828px;"><div class="gtx-trans-icon">&nbsp;</div></div>
]]>
