                <![CDATA[<p>由 Coinbase Ventures 主导的 Base 生态基金，旨在建构 L2 链 – Base 上的新世代专案，日前宣布其第一批投资名单。这次投资源自三月该基金提出的三个方向：Flatcoin、链上声誉、链上限价订单簿（LOB）交易所、更安全的 DeFi。<a href="https://base.mirror.xyz/yxd0L-FlWCto53pDaxIkEBdkgavvXJk4S3O_5-I33No" target="_blank" rel="noopener">获得投资的六个专案</a>，是从 800 份申请中脱颖而出：Avantis、BSX、Onboard、OpenCover、Paragraph 和 Truflation。</p><p>(<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeiSAod4PAbXlvvDGtHWu-GqzGpvHYfaTQR2f77AawD7GYc4Q/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">向 Coinbase 申请 Base 生态基金</a>)</p><p>以下是它们的介绍：</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/base-ecosystem-fund-announces-first-six-investment#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-651d09363008b"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
