                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-651d09363008b"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/base-ecosystem-fund-announces-first-six-investment/#100x_%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E8%88%87_RWA%EF%BC%9AAvantis" title="100x 交易加密货币与 RWA：Avantis">100x 交易加密货币与 RWA：Avantis</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/base-ecosystem-fund-announces-first-six-investment/#%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%96%E9%99%90%E5%83%B9%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E7%B0%BF%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%EF%BC%9ABSX" title="去中心化限价订单簿交易所：BSX">去中心化限价订单簿交易所：BSX</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/base-ecosystem-fund-announces-first-six-investment/#Onboard" title="Onboard">Onboard</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4" href="https://abmedia.io/base-ecosystem-fund-announces-first-six-investment/#OpenCover" title="OpenCover">OpenCover</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5" href="https://abmedia.io/base-ecosystem-fund-announces-first-six-investment/#Paragraph" title="Paragraph">Paragraph</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6" href="https://abmedia.io/base-ecosystem-fund-announces-first-six-investment/#Truflation" title="Truflation">Truflation</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="100x_%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E8%88%87_RWA%EF%BC%9AAvantis"></span>100x 交易加密货币与 RWA：<a href="https://www.avantisfi.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Avantis</a><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Avantis 是一个基于预言机的合成衍生品协议，用户可以以高达 100 倍的杠杆交易加密货币和现实世界资产 (RWA)，并借由提供 USDC 流动性作为造市商来获得收益。</p><p>Base 生态基金喜欢 Avantis 的仅支援 USDC 的简单设计以及风险管理周到考虑 (批次和灵活锁定)。</p><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-78327 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/avantis-scaled.webp?resize=2560%2C1657&amp;ssl=1" alt="avantis" width="2560" height="1657" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/avantis-scaled.webp?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/avantis-scaled.webp?resize=300%2C194&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/avantis-scaled.webp?resize=1024%2C663&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/avantis-scaled.webp?resize=600%2C388&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/avantis-scaled.webp?resize=768%2C497&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/avantis-scaled.webp?resize=1536%2C994&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/avantis-scaled.webp?resize=2048%2C1326&amp;ssl=1 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%96%E9%99%90%E5%83%B9%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E7%B0%BF%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%EF%BC%9ABSX"></span>去中心化限价订单簿交易所：<a href="https://www.bsx.exchange/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BSX</a><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>BSX 正在构建一个用户可以多空杠杆交易的去中心化限价订单簿。</p><p>Base 生态基金认为，链上交易应由各种市场结构的支援，无论是 AMM、订单簿还是任何其他新颖结构。它对 BSX 结合 CeFi 交易体验和 DeFi 的安全性感到期待。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Onboard"></span><a href="https://www.onboard.xyz/">Onboard</a><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Onboard 为用户提供了一种链上、自托管的方式，透过他们自己的 MPC 钱包和智能合约进行加密货币出入金，以点对点的方式进行。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="OpenCover"></span><a href="https://opencover.com/">OpenCover</a><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>OpenCover 是第一个与 Nexus Mutual 等保险公司合作的 L2 保险总和平台，旨在保护 DeFi 用户免受链上风险，如：智能合约被攻击和预言机故障。OpenCover 还提供用户在交易时提供链上保险选择，以使链上风险管理对所有人变得容易、可负担。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Paragraph"></span><a href="https://paragraph.xyz/">Paragraph</a><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Paragraph 是一个链上创作者平台，帮助创作者发布、分享并在其内容建立业务，使用无许可协议来加速增长和收益潜力。Paragraph 利用新颖的链上机制，例如：使创作者能够将贴文变成可收藏品、向钱包地址发送新闻通讯、透过会员权益实现盈利，以及利用去中心化社交协议 (例如：Farcaster、Lens、XMTP）来建立和培养其社群。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Truflation"></span><a href="https://truflation.com/">Truflation</a><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Truflation 是一个链上金融预言机，通过实时从 1800 万个点和 40 多个数据来源编制数据，提供自动和独立的每日通膨报吿 (即 CPI 指数)。这代表了对代币通膨的更高保真度描述，与目前的方法相比，该方法自 1998 年以来几乎未有变化，每月只报告一次。</p><div id="gtx-trans" style="position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 1505.63px;"><div class="gtx-trans-icon">&nbsp;</div></div>
]]>
